    <h2>How to Safely Use Good & Gather Chocolate Chips in Gluten-Free Baking</h2>

    <p>Even if your chocolate chips are gluten-free, cross-contamination can still occur during the baking process. Here are some tips to ensure that your baked goods remain gluten-free:</p>

    <ul>
