        <li><strong>Check for Cross-Contamination Warnings:</strong> Some products may be processed in facilities that also handle gluten-containing ingredients. Look for warnings on the packaging if this is a concern.</li>
        <li><strong>Store Separately:</strong> Store your gluten-free ingredients, including chocolate chips, in a separate area of your pantry to avoid accidental contamination.</li>
    </ul>

